br />\n<br />\n6.咁我想訂可以去邊度訂?<br />\n大家去返第一個post 頭post 寫左<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/245395/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/245395/page/1</a><br />\n其實通常都係孤仔同精品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n7. 咁買完點擺Figure 好?<br />\n屋企有位 整個展示盒玩下先<br />\n(大陸) 淘寶 ( 唔想用大陸野, 可以無視)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別訂造- 移不動<br />\n可以SD 圖整特定的 仲有雕刻 有燈<br />\n<a href=\"https://ybdzsh.taobao.com/shop/view_shop.htm?shop_id=35283664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fybdzsh.taobao.com%2Fshop%2Fview_shop.htm%3Fshop_id%3D35283664&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnP7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=6b8cdb96\" target=\"_blank\">https://ybdzsh.taobao.com/shop/view_shop.htm?shop_id=35283664</a><br />\n<br />\n信緯傢俬( from 米鋪)<br />\n訂造高櫃,玻璃雙門<br />\n無錢(買完無錢...)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開門式書櫃.."},{"pid":"aadf2f8226074c3603c4f5abd59753e7954c46fd","tid":1063968,"uid":31961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"8.咁保養自己心愛的Figure, 有無咩要留意呢? (重要)<br />\n綜合左各位意見同埋我網上google研究之後, 有以下幾點需要留意:<br />\nPVC Figure本身就會劣化(出油).. <br />\n(原文:GOOD SMILE SHANGHAI官方微博)<br />\n而主要加速劣化的原因: (from abcvpn666)<br />\n1.) 陽光, 強光<br />\n2.) 溫度<br />\n3.) 濕度 (影響埋發霉, 香港會煩埋呢樣)<br />\n4.) 鹽份 (海邊...應該都會影響埋發霉)<br />\n5.) 通唔通風<br />\n<br />\n唔Hi係掛, 咁我既 Figure 點算好...<br />\n咁大家又唔洗太驚,以下提供幾種方法<br />\n<br />\n歐洲人解決方法:<br />\nKEEP住開冷氣同抽濕<br />\n普通人的解決方法:<br />\n-Figure 盡量遠離陽光<br />\n-避免長期 &quot; 密封 &quot; 保存（盡量不要一直關在盒子里<br />\n得閒開黎睇睇先<br />\n<br />\n嘩, 放出黎會咁樣樣<br />\n咁唔開盒咪得<br />\n你咁諗就錯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為留意返上面避免長期 &quot; 密封 &quot; 保存（盡量不要一直關在盒子里）<br />\n通埋 加速劣化原因(通唔通風)<br />\n即是話唔開都會GG... <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n9.咁想快人一步知道或者親身感受可以去咩展呢?<br />\nWonder Festival(WF)應該最多廠商參加<br />\n一年通常有兩次 係日本<br />\n<a href=\"http://wf.kaiyodo.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwf.kaiyodo.net%2F&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnP7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=cb77b460\" target=\"_blank\">http://wf.kaiyodo.net/</a><br />\n一次WF(冬) 通常2月<br />\n一次WF(夏)通常7月<br />\n去唔到都唔緊要<br />\n呢度都會報導<br />\n<a href=\"http://hobby.dengeki.com/event/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhobby.dengeki.com%2Fevent%2F&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnP7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=4967a1f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hobby.dengeki.com/event/</a> (日本)<br />\n<br />\n暫時只係諗到咁多<br />\n有咩正figure 不妨post 黎睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歡迎大家討論Figure<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一切源於愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc1d313ed53d4858c3ec58add6f57458607ae18","tid":1063968,"uid":46901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T11:52:03.000Z","msg":"春梅delayed <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}